# Title: HackTool - Htran/NATBypass Execution
# Author: Florian Roth (Nextron Systems)
# Date: 2022-12-27
# Level: high
# Description: Detects executable names or flags used by Htran or Htran-like tools (e.g. NATBypass)
# MITRE Tactic: Command and Control
# Tags: attack.command-and-control, attack.t1090, attack.s0040
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/process_creation/proc_creation_win_hktl_htran_or_natbypass.yml

CommandLine IN ("*.exe -tran *", "*.exe -slave *") OR Image IN ("*\\htran.exe", "*\\lcx.exe")